<h3 data-start="149" data-end="186">📱 Testing Karne Ke Best Methods:</h3>
<h4 data-start="188" data-end="242">1️⃣ <strong data-start="197" data-end="237">TestFlight (Best for iPhone Testing)</strong> 🍏</h4>
<p data-start="243" data-end="382">👉 Apple ka official testing platform hai.<br data-start="285" data-end="288">
✔ App upload karo<br data-start="305" data-end="308">
✔ Spain ke tester ka email add karo<br data-start="343" data-end="346">
✔ Wo Spain se app install kar lega</p>
<p data-start="384" data-end="413">👉 Ye best &amp; safe method hai.</p>
<hr data-start="415" data-end="418">
<h4 data-start="420" data-end="468">2️⃣ <strong data-start="429" data-end="463">Live Server / Cloud Deployment</strong> ☁️</h4>
<ul data-start="469" data-end="551">
<li data-start="469" data-end="506">
<p data-start="471" data-end="506">App ko cloud server par host karo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="507" data-end="551">
<p data-start="509" data-end="551">Spain ka user directly app access karega</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="553" data-end="573">Popular platforms:</p>
<ul data-start="574" data-end="605">
<li data-start="574" data-end="581">
<p data-start="576" data-end="581">AWS</p>
</li>
<li data-start="582" data-end="594">
<p data-start="584" data-end="594">Firebase</p>
</li>
<li data-start="595" data-end="605">
<p data-start="597" data-end="605">Vercel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="607" data-end="610">
<h4 data-start="612" data-end="650">3️⃣ <strong data-start="621" data-end="645">Remote Testing Tools</strong> 💻</h4>
<ul data-start="651" data-end="712">
<li data-start="651" data-end="712">
<p data-start="653" data-end="676">Browser apps ke liye:</p>
<ul data-start="679" data-end="712">
<li data-start="679" data-end="695">
<p data-start="681" data-end="695">BrowserStack</p>
</li>
<li data-start="698" data-end="712">
<p data-start="700" data-end="712">LambdaTest</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="714" data-end="717">
<h3 data-start="719" data-end="743">⚠️ Important Points:</h3>
<ul data-start="744" data-end="900">
<li data-start="744" data-end="822">
<p data-start="746" data-end="822">Spain wale iPhone user ka Apple ID / Email chahiye testing invite ke liye.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="823" data-end="900">
<p data-start="825" data-end="900">Certificate + Provisioning profile setup karna hota hai (iOS apps ke liye).</p>
</li>
</ul>
