<h3 data-start="72" data-end="95">💰 <strong data-start="79" data-end="95">Free Methods</strong></h3>
<p data-start="96" data-end="140">👍 <strong data-start="99" data-end="138">TestFlight (Apple ka official tool)</strong></p>
<ul data-start="141" data-end="258">
<li data-start="141" data-end="153">
<p data-start="143" data-end="153">Free hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="154" data-end="202">
<p data-start="156" data-end="202">Spain ke iPhone user ko invite bhej sakte ho</p>
</li>
<li data-start="203" data-end="258">
<p data-start="205" data-end="258">Apple Developer account free testing limit deta hai</p>
</li>
</ul>
