div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="5d28b1ea-4e1e-4554-b20d-f9c62004a2a2" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-mini" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="143">Haan, <strong data-start="6" data-end="65">aap apna local server bana kar bhi testing kar sakte ho</strong>, lekin Pakistan se Spain wale iPhone par direct access thoda tricky hai. 😅</p>
<p data-start="145" data-end="186">Main options step by step bata raha hoon:</p>
<hr data-start="188" data-end="191">
<h3 data-start="193" data-end="260">1️⃣ <strong data-start="201" data-end="258">Local Server + Ngrok / Localtunnel (Best Free Option)</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="261" data-end="481">
<li data-start="261" data-end="330">
<p data-start="263" data-end="330"><strong data-start="263" data-end="279">Local server</strong> apne PC par run karo (Node.js, PHP, Python etc.)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="331" data-end="426">
<p data-start="333" data-end="426"><strong data-start="333" data-end="342">Ngrok</strong> ya <strong data-start="346" data-end="361">Localtunnel</strong> use karo → ye aapke local server ko <strong data-start="398" data-end="412">public URL</strong> de deta hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="427" data-end="481">
<p data-start="429" data-end="481">Spain wala iPhone is URL se app test kar sakta hai</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="483" data-end="495"><strong data-start="483" data-end="493">Steps:</strong></p>
<ol data-start="496" data-end="710">
<li data-start="496" data-end="549">
<p data-start="499" data-end="549">Apne PC par server start karo (<code data-start="530" data-end="546">localhost:3000</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="550" data-end="587">
<p data-start="553" data-end="587">Install Ngrok: <code data-start="568" data-end="585">ngrok http 3000</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="588" data-end="659">
<p data-start="591" data-end="659">Ngrok aapko ek public URL dega (jaise <code data-start="629" data-end="656">https://abcd1234.ngrok.io</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="660" data-end="710">
<p data-start="663" data-end="710">Spain user is URL par iPhone se access karega</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="712" data-end="771">✅ Free method hai (Ngrok free tier limited time ke liye).</p>
<hr data-start="773" data-end="776">
<h3 data-start="778" data-end="810">2️⃣ <strong data-start="786" data-end="808">VPN + Local Server</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="811" data-end="953">
<li data-start="811" data-end="852">
<p data-start="813" data-end="852">Pakistan se Spain ka IP simulate karo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="853" data-end="898">
<p data-start="855" data-end="898">Spain iPhone se local server ko test karo</p>
</li>
<li data-start="899" data-end="953">
<p data-start="901" data-end="953">Thoda complex hai, beginner ke liye nahi recommend</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="955" data-end="958">
<h3 data-start="960" data-end="1019">3️⃣ <strong data-start="968" data-end="1017">Cloud Server (Recommended for Smooth Testing)</strong></h3>
<ul data-start="1020" data-end="1146">
<li data-start="1020" data-end="1079">
<p data-start="1022" data-end="1079">Agar frequent testing chahiye → local server tricky hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1080" data-end="1146">
<p data-start="1082" data-end="1146">Cloud server par host karo → Spain user directly access karega</p>
</li>
</ul>
