<p data-start="1153" data-end="1170">💡 <strong data-start="1156" data-end="1168">Summary:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1171" data-end="1272">
<li data-start="1171" data-end="1214">
<p data-start="1173" data-end="1214">Quick &amp; free → <strong data-start="1188" data-end="1212">Ngrok + local server</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1215" data-end="1272">
<p data-start="1217" data-end="1272">Stable &amp; professional → <strong data-start="1241" data-end="1270">Cloud server + TestFlight</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
