ssages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="237f34f1-3bb2-4ebd-98c0-32b3601b1a71" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-2" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[1px]"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="106">✅ <strong data-start="2" data-end="19">Short Answer:</strong><br data-start="19" data-end="22">
Ngrok ke <strong data-start="31" data-end="101">ek hi public link se aap multiple mobiles par testing kar sakte ho</strong> 👍</p>
<hr data-start="108" data-end="111">
<h2 data-start="113" data-end="133">📱 Kitne mobiles?</h2>
<h3 data-start="135" data-end="157">🔹 Free Ngrok Plan</h3>
<ul data-start="158" data-end="456">
<li data-start="158" data-end="216">
<p data-start="160" data-end="216">Ek time par <strong data-start="172" data-end="192">multiple devices</strong> access kar sakte hain</p>
</li>
<li data-start="217" data-end="275">
<p data-start="219" data-end="275">Spain, Pakistan, kisi bhi country se open ho sakta hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="276" data-end="312">
<p data-start="278" data-end="312">Koi fixed mobile limit nahi hoti</p>
</li>
<li data-start="313" data-end="456">
<p data-start="315" data-end="321">Lekin:</p>
<ul data-start="324" data-end="456">
<li data-start="324" data-end="375">
<p data-start="326" data-end="375">Agar traffic zyada ho jaye to slow ho sakta hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="378" data-end="410">
<p data-start="380" data-end="410">Session timeout ho sakta hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="413" data-end="456">
<p data-start="415" data-end="456">Restart karoge to link change ho jayega</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="458" data-end="461">
<h2 data-start="463" data-end="489">⚠️ Important Limitation</h2>
<p data-start="490" data-end="506">Free version me:</p>
<ul data-start="507" data-end="617">
<li data-start="507" data-end="545">
<p data-start="509" data-end="545">Ek hi active tunnel chal sakta hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="546" data-end="581">
<p data-start="548" data-end="581">URL restart par change hota hai</p>
</li>
<li data-start="582" data-end="617">
<p data-start="584" data-end="617">Heavy traffic allowed nahi hota</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="619" data-end="622">
<h2 data-start="624" data-end="647">🎯 Practical Example</h2>
<p data-start="648" data-end="769">Agar aap link 5–10 logon ko bhej do → sab open kar sakte hain<br data-start="709" data-end="712">
Agar 100 log ek sath open karein → slow ho sakta hai 😅</p>
<hr data-start="771" data-end="774">
<h2 data-start="776" data-end="792">🔥 Pro Advice</h2>
<p data-start="793" data-end="861">Testing ke liye perfect hai<br data-start="820" data-end="823">
Production / public app ke liye nahi</p>
<hr data-start="863" data-end="866">
<p data-start="868" data-end="1027">Agar chaho to main aapko bata sakta hoon:<br>
👉 Kaise ek hi link permanent banayein<br data-start="948" data-end="951">
👉 Kaise speed improve karein<br data-start="980" data-end="983">
👉 Kaise secure karein (password protection)</p>
